  "title": "6723 - Audit supervisor [Beach Road | 5 days | External audit]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Audit Supervisor</strong></p>\n<p>5 days<br>\n0830am - 1730pm<br>\n$4,000-$5,000<br>\nBeach Road</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, co-ordinate and supervisor various audit assignments for review by the engagement manager or partner.</li>\n  <li>Manage a portfolio of engagements to deliver high quality audit services.</li>\n  <li>Provide leadership on audit engagements which include client acceptance process, engagement planning, execution and finalisation of an audit engagement.</li>\n  <li>Fully accountable for the audit engagement and ensures that the engagement progress against budget and timeline is closely monitored.</li>\n  <li>Manages a portfolio of engagements which includes client acceptance, engagement planning, execution and finalization of an audit engagement.</li>\n  <li>Fully accountable for the audit engagement and ensures that the engagement progress against budget and timeline is closely monitored.</li>\n  <li>Serves to develop and maintain long-term client relationships and value-add to the audit firm by identifying new business development opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Review and provides key technical expertise to ensure the quality of audit work performed is in compliance with professional standards and requirements.</li>\n  <li>Contributes towards continuous improvement in audit methodology and process.</li>\n  <li>Assume a greater role in professional development activities such as training, staff recruitment and resource planning.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor's Degree or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Minimum 4 years of working experience as Audit supervisor.</li>\n  <li>Experience in IPOs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Chaw Chiaw Han, Reg No：R22106723 |</strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd, EA No：14c7279</strong></p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Email: supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</strong></p>",
